trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintServer"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintServerProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> property of a print system object, including casing.
